3. RLS behavioural verification (as NOSUPERUSER NOBYPASSRLS role)
================================================================================

  Created locally in the throwaway because `--no-privileges` strips GRANTs:
    CREATE ROLE rls_test_role NOSUPERUSER NOBYPASSRLS LOGIN;
    GRANT SELECT ON products, sales, tenants TO rls_test_role;

  As rls_test_role, NO `app.tenant_id` set:
    SELECT count(*) FROM products  →  0  ✅ (RLS hides every row)

  As rls_test_role, `app.tenant_id` set to tenant e8335de6-0a2a-4ad9-a32e-0c9f49b56c15:
    SELECT count(*) FROM products  →  1  ✅ (tenant-scoped reads work)

